net.casper.data.model

Class CDataResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.casper.data.model.CDataResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AutoCloseable, ResultSet, Wrapper

    public class CDataResultSet
extends Object
implements ResultSet, Serializable
    This is a JDBC ResultSet-compliant implementation of the casper rowset. The implementation of this wrapper will allow applications that rely upon JDBC resultsets to plug into the casper datasets framework more or less seamlessly.

    Note: there are a number of methods that have been left as no-op or return "null" values. Please feel free to flesh out the implementation. Requires Java 1.4 (or later).
    Since:
    v1.0
    Version:
    $Revision: 111 $
    Author:
    Jonathan Liang
